	<h1 class="title">25 年后，《东京爱情故事》的续集来了</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/4369/small/4369.jpg?1419239008" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">晏文静 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2016-02-16 15:22:30 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/22356/medium/22356.jpg?1455603693" alt="" />			
	</div>
